oads.wordpress.org/plugin/debug-bar-console.0.2.zip\";s:3:\"0.3\";s:64:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/debug-bar-console.0.3.zip\";s:5:\"trunk\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/debug-bar-console.zip\";}s:11:\"donate_link\";s:0:\"\";}', 'no'),
